  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Transforming Local Fishermen Into Coral Gardeners</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project trains and certifies local fishermen as coral gardeners, boat captains, scuba divers and artisans.Its continued expansion in the country will provide a positive example for replication in other tourism destinations.Our goal is to reduce over-fishing on the reef while providing stable tourism jobs for local fishermen and their families.Corals are one of the species most affected by climate change.By reducing fishing pressure and increasing coral cover,we help build reef resiliency.</narrative>
  </description>
